 (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/internals/metrics/ConsumerRebalanceMetricsManager.java) - Concrete implementation extending RebalanceMetricsManager to track consumer rebalance metrics including latency (avg/max/total), rebalance rate, and failed rebalance statistics.\n3. ShareRebalanceMetricsManager (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/internals/metrics/ShareRebalanceMetricsManager.java) - Concrete implementation extending RebalanceMetricsManager for share consumer rebalance metrics tracking.\n4. RebalanceCallbackMetricsManager (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/internals/metrics/RebalanceCallbackMetricsManager.java) - Tracks metrics for rebalance listener callback execution (partition revoked/assigned/lost latency measurements).\n\nThese classes work together to implement the consumer group rebalance protocol, managing callback invocation, state transitions, and performance metrics collection across both classic consumer group protocol and Kafka Streams group protocol implementations."
